        "text_Xb7E6M": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "kicker": "Please Keep in Mind...",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>Our pricing guidelines are rough estimates. Seasonality and style will affect pricing and your end payout. </p><p>Low priced items under $20 are ineligible for consignment as their processing costs are greater than their payouts. </p><p>You are still welcome to send them in for TriedEq to donate, upcycle, recycle or resell as we see fit.</p><p></p>",
