    "section_richtext_F43tBc": {
      "type": "section-richtext",
      "blocks": {
        "icon_text_LXnHbV": {
          "type": "icon-text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "kicker_size": 3,
            "heading_size": 6,
            "text_size": 4,
            "items_per_row": "3",
            "icon_color": "#4b4b4b",
            "icon_size": 24,
            "icon_name_1": "icon-legal",
            "icon_kicker_1": "Research & Photograpy",
            "icon_heading_1": "Processing",
            "icon_text_1": "<p>Our team does extensive market research to create the most accurate product description for your item. We then style and photograph your item for optimal selling.</p>",
            "icon_name_2": "icon-dollar",
            "icon_kicker_2": "Launch & Selling",
            "icon_heading_2": "Listing",
            "icon_text_2": "<p>Once the listing has been written, uploaded, and double-checked, it is pushed live and promoted on our 'New Arrivals' section. We utilize organic and paid ads, email and SMS marketing, and have a brick-and-mortar store.</p>",
            "icon_name_3": "icon-shipment",
            "icon_kicker_3": "Shipping & Payment",
            "icon_heading_3": "Final Steps",
            "icon_text_3": "<p>Your item has been purchased! We ship it directly from our store to its new owner. We wait for the return window to pass and you receive payment one month delayed from the month the item sold.</p>",
            "icon_name_4": "none",
